intent.user_query: Which customer has the highest number of sales transactions?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName, COUNT(s.SaleID) AS NumberOfSales FROM fitness_db.Customers c JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON c.CustomerID = s.CustomerID GROUP BY c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName ORDER BY NumberOfSales DESC LIMIT 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName, COUNT(s.SaleID) AS NumberOfSales FROM fitness_db.Customers c JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON c.CustomerID = s.CustomerID GROUP BY c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName ORDER BY NumberOfSales DESC LIMIT 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
